body:
**This module has added the following items:**
1. A versatile tool that can switch between multiple modes and provide various BUFF and options; 
2. A parallel supported alloy furnace; 
3. When installing the thermal series, additional upgrade components and parallel components will be provided; 
4. Add nine new alloys and corresponding gears and glass for synthesis; 
5. Two dimensional teleporters: Blocks already enclosed within the dimension (available in odd and even styles), perpetual day, customizable border blocks, filled blocks, and center point blocks. 

**At the same time, the following Modifications are attached:**
1. Modify Mek upgrade quantity limit, and the quantity and upgrade effect multiplier can be modified through the configuration file; 
2. Cancelled the rendering animation of plant pots and leaky plant pots, and supported modifying the plant pot magnification through configuration files; 
3. Support customizing the template multiplier of the assembly matrix template core through configuration files.

